# Context

## Background
Moved site-level JSON-LD generation out of theme templates and starter scaffolds into the site pipeline so WebSite, Organization, WebPage, and breadcrumb data are derived from canonical config and render context.

## Why This Way
This removes hardcoded theme-specific schema values, keeps answer-specific schema generation intact, and makes site-wide structured data automatic for pages and sections.

## Gotchas
Answer pages still emit a separate answer-specific JSON-LD document and /schema.json output; site-wide and answer-specific schema are intentionally layered.

